Credentials
Data are retrieve from ESGF through the Institut Pierre-Simon Laplace node. You need first to create an account on this page (create account link at corner right). Then you‚Äôll need to register credentials locally to use the workflow. For that use a credentials_esgf yaml file reported in config.yml with keys openid and pwd. For example using bash in linux:
openid=https://esgf-node.ipsl.upmc.fr/esgf-idp/openid/{user}
pwd={pwd}
echo -e "openid: $openid\npwd: $pwd" &gt; config/credentials_esgf.yml
